1.title: Redneck Sharktank

episode of.title: Billy Bob's Gags to Riches (TV Series 2014– )

1.plot: Jonah White, CEO of Billy Bob Products is looking to invest in the next million-dollar gag idea. Aspiring inventors seeking the American dream pitch Jonah and team in hopes of striking a deal. Bizarre to many, to Jonah- it's big business.

2.title: Crash for Cash

episode of.title: Billy Bob's Gags to Riches (TV Series 2014– )

2.plot: Billy Bob receives a potentially massive order for an impulse buy item. Certified redneck, Danny Trone, convinces Jonah to join him in a Demolition Derby. The Redneck Think Tank seeks out a little motherly advice to help them with a new prototype.

3.title: Up Pitch Creek

episode of.title: Billy Bob's Gags to Riches (TV Series 2014– )

3.plot: Faced with lagging summertime sales Jonah looks to revitalize his product line when first time inventors pitch a slew of new ideas. A suitcase folding Tote Boat, the Cool Air Cap, and the Redneck iPad are merely a few up for negotiations.

4.title: The Buck Starts Here

episode of.title: Billy Bob's Gags to Riches (TV Series 2014– )

4.plot: Jonah wants to launch a redneck hunting novelty item; triple-barrel shotgun; Insta-Buck kit; florescent toilet paper.

5.title: Trial by Fire

episode of.title: Billy Bob's Gags to Riches (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: When a disgruntled client returns $20,000 worth of gag items Jonah lays down the law at Billy Bob headquarters. Eager to recoup his losses Jonah goes all in on a hot new product hoping to not get burned.

6.title: Pitch & Pray

episode of.title: Billy Bob's Gags to Riches (TV Series 2014– )

6.plot: In the Season Finale the pressure mounts as Jonah's quest for the next million-dollar gag item nears its end. With the deadline looming and his catalogue cover page still empty, anxious inventors line up for their last shot of fame and fortune.

-1.title: Pilot

episode of.title: Billy Bob's Gags to Riches (TV Series 2014– )

-1.plot: Eccentric redneck millionaire Jonah White is always on the lookout for the next big idea, that is when he's not keeping a watchful eye on his chaotic but adorable family.

imdb.plot outline: Meet Jonah White, novelty king and owner of Billy Bob World in Hardin, Illinois - a place where redneck inventors can pitch their best ideas in hopes of striking it rich. After building an empire on his own invention - fake hillbilly buck teeth - Jonah has accomplished the America dream, creating a booming business with over 300-products sold throughout the world. Now, redneck inventors from all over are coming to Billy Bob World to pitch Jonah their own outrageous ideas for a piece of the pie.
